{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-405-a-rectangular-tiling","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 405: Raspoređivanje pravougaonika sa pločicama","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Želimo da nacrtamo pravougaonik čija je dužina dvostruka njegove širine.</p>\n<p>Neka $T(0)$ bude raspored koji sadrži samo jedan pravougaonik.</p>\n<p>Za $n > 0$, neka se $T(n)$ dobije iz $T(n-1)$ promenom svih pločica na sledeći način:</p>\n<img alt=\"obtaining T(n) from T(n - 1)\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/a-rectangular-tiling-1.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Grafik prikazuje $T(n)$ za $n$ od 0 do 5:</p>\n<img alt=\"animation with tilings T(n) for n from 0 to 5\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/a-rectangular-tiling-2.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka je $f(n)$ broj tačaka gde se četiri pločice sastaju u $T(n)$. Na primer, $f(1) = 0$, $f(4) = 82$ i $f({10}^9)\\bmod {17}^7 = 126\\,897\\,180$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $f({10}^k)$ za $k = {10}^{18}$, prikaži svoj rezultat po modulu ${17}^7$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5021000cf542c510014","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302073,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-405-a-rectangular-tiling"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function rectangularTiling() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nrectangularTiling();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>rectangularTiling()</code> treba da vrati <code>237696125</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(rectangularTiling(), 237696125);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-405-a-rectangular-tiling","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-406-guessing-game","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-404-crisscross-ellipses","id":"5900f5021000cf542c510014","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-405-a-rectangular-tiling"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}